30:06.060 --> 30:07.260
we had all of these projects.

30:07.260 --> 30:10.500
We had Wine and Mono and all of these attempts

30:10.500 --> 30:15.420
to just coexist in a world that was dominated by Microsoft.

30:15.420 --> 30:18.060
And we finally get through all of that.

30:18.060 --> 30:21.380
