31:22.500 --> 31:24.940
the closed source software they sell.

31:24.940 --> 31:29.460
They have been more like IBM for a very long time

31:29.460 --> 31:31.140
than we'd like to acknowledge,

31:31.140 --> 31:33.580
because we like to look at the things that they do

31:33.580 --> 31:37.940
