31:45.500 --> 31:48.220
and so many other fundamental technologies,

31:48.220 --> 31:49.540
Flatpak, et cetera, et cetera,

31:49.540 --> 31:52.980
that don't really seem to have a direct cloud angle,

31:52.980 --> 31:55.620
don't have a direct services industry angle,

31:55.620 --> 31:58.100
